	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Here's how to add an object:<br /><br />1: Draw a sprite using a graphics editor.<br />2: In &quot;animation.txt&quot; write the metasprite data for the sprite.  I'll explain the format when I have time.<br />3: In &quot;object.txt&quot; write the object's routine.  All that needs to be done in the routine is store the address of the metasprite data in the &quot;requested metasprite&quot; variable.<br />4: Look for the list of level objects, and insert the name of the object routine there, along with a few other things that I'll explain Tomorrow.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

